description: Enforce HL2RP suffix on new HL2RP prototypes
globs: Resources/Prototypes/HL2RP/**/*.yml
alwaysApply: false
---

# HL2RP Prototype Suffix

- Every new prototype created in `Resources/Prototypes/HL2RP/` must include `suffix: HL2RP`.
- Place `suffix: HL2RP` near the top-level prototype fields for readability and consistency.
- If a file contains multiple new prototypes, each one must have this suffix.

## Example

```yaml
# ❌ BAD
- type: entity
  id: CIDCard
  name: CID card

# ✅ GOOD
- type: entity
  id: CIDCard
  suffix: HL2RP
  name: CID card
```
